1
00:00:38,820 --> 00:00:40,820
=Visage and Soul=

2
00:00:40,820 --> 00:00:43,040
(The "Different Her"
Trilogy on Women's Relationships)

3
00:00:44,720 --> 00:00:47,640
=Episode 9=

4
00:00:52,760 --> 00:00:54,440
(She celebrated my birthday today.)

5
00:00:56,880 --> 00:00:59,040
(But if she finds out
it's actually your birthday,)

6
00:00:59,640 --> 00:01:00,960
(and realizes I'm not you,)

7
00:01:02,760 --> 00:01:04,160
(will she be heartbroken?)

8
00:01:06,280 --> 00:01:06,960
(No.)

9
00:01:07,400 --> 00:01:08,760
(Right now, I am you.)

10
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:11,960
(I have to find out the
truth for all of you.)

11
00:01:12,640 --> 00:01:13,880
(I have to find out)

12
00:01:13,880 --> 00:01:15,640
(what exactly happened back then.)

13
00:01:20,920 --> 00:01:21,640
(Ji Ran.)

14
00:01:22,600 --> 00:01:23,760
(Happy birthday.)

15
00:01:34,160 --> 00:01:35,000
What's wrong?

16
00:01:39,160 --> 00:01:40,560
I don't want to lie to her anymore.

17
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:42,360
Tomorrow, I'm going
to tell her the truth.

18
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:44,320
No matter how it ends.

19
00:01:47,320 --> 00:01:49,160
Every time she calls me Qin Yu,

20
00:01:49,160 --> 00:01:51,000
I feel like I'm deceiving her feelings.

21
00:01:54,360 --> 00:01:55,600
What worries me most right now

22
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:58,400
is that she doesn't
really like me at all,

23
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:02,800
but she likes the paintings you created.

24
00:02:07,640 --> 00:02:08,960
What matters most is the heart.

25
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:11,400
When you love someone,
it's about the true feelings,

26
00:02:11,720 --> 00:02:12,800
not anything else.

27
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:16,200
Your feelings for her are real,

28
00:02:16,200 --> 00:02:18,000
and her feelings for
you are genuine too.

29
00:02:18,200 --> 00:02:19,200
That's enough.

30
00:02:21,760 --> 00:02:22,880
As for everything else,

31
00:02:22,880 --> 00:02:24,200
it's really not that important.

32
00:03:09,720 --> 00:03:11,200
How did you get in here?

33
00:03:11,200 --> 00:03:12,280
I paid for the room.

34
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:13,320
I can come in whenever I want.

35
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:20,120
Come on, man. I told you to deceive her,

36
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:22,040
not fall in love with her.

37
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:27,040
Mr. Qiao.

38
00:03:29,040 --> 00:03:30,520
That's easy for you to say.

39
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:31,880
If I didn't romance her,

40
00:03:31,880 --> 00:03:33,160
how would I get her
to sign the agreement?

41
00:03:36,440 --> 00:03:38,800
I'm running out of patience, sweetheart.

42
00:03:40,760 --> 00:03:41,920
I'll speed things up.

43
00:03:44,160 --> 00:03:46,360
Focus on the art exhibition.

44
00:03:55,080 --> 00:03:57,000
You don't seriously want
to be my brother-in-law, do you?

45
00:04:57,320 --> 00:04:58,380
(Rizhao Sun Park Travel Guide)

46
00:04:58,380 --> 00:05:02,440
♪Everything was so beautiful
in my memories♪

47
00:05:04,143 --> 00:05:09,120
♪In every photo,
you were always smiling♪

48
00:05:11,018 --> 00:05:15,764
♪And that little cat by the window♪

49
00:05:17,112 --> 00:05:22,520
♪Always stretching lazily♪

50
00:05:24,772 --> 00:05:29,800
♪Sometimes I dream
about it without realizing♪

51
00:05:31,599 --> 00:05:37,120
♪About us frozen in that embrace♪

52
00:05:38,455 --> 00:05:43,520
♪And somehow, tears always come♪

53
00:05:44,431 --> 00:05:50,000
♪As that old song
echoes in my ears again♪

54
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:01,880
Hey!

55
00:06:19,960 --> 00:06:20,840
Liar!

56
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:26,480
Sc*mbag!

57
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:29,480
J*rk!

58
00:06:53,280 --> 00:06:54,800
Either talk, or get out of the car.

59
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:56,880
And stay out of my life for good.

60
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:01,240
You're right.

61
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,640
I am a liar.

62
00:07:04,200 --> 00:07:05,760
And the lies I've told you

63
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:08,480
are far more than you
could ever imagine.

64
00:07:14,400 --> 00:07:15,480
I'm not Qin Yu.

65
00:07:18,200 --> 00:07:19,560
My real name is Ji Ran.

66
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:22,440
Qin Yu was my best friend in college.

67
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:24,440
He loved painting.

68
00:07:25,320 --> 00:07:26,320
I loved sports.

69
00:07:29,080 --> 00:07:31,000
The first time we met,

70
00:07:32,640 --> 00:07:34,720
somehow, you mistook me for Qin Yu.

71
00:07:36,440 --> 00:07:37,720
And you said you liked my paintings.

72
00:07:41,160 --> 00:07:43,800
The truth is, I used to
be a very honest person.

73
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:48,280
But at that moment,

74
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:54,800
I decided to tell the
first lie of my life.

75
00:08:04,960 --> 00:08:06,360
Later, we got together.

76
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:08,200
I was very happy.

77
00:08:13,120 --> 00:08:14,440
But I was also terrified.

78
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:18,280
I was terrified that one day,
it would all come out.

79
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:20,400
And sure enough,

80
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:24,200
you eventually learned the truth.

81
00:08:25,920 --> 00:08:27,000
You were furious.

82
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:30,240
And we broke up.

83
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:34,720
After we broke up,

84
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:37,240
I went abroad.

85
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:42,040
I worked hard to become a better artist.

86
00:08:44,920 --> 00:08:46,240
Hoping that one day,

87
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:48,440
I could become someone you'd love.

88
00:08:54,080 --> 00:08:55,040
Then later,

89
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:57,640
I heard about your accident.

90
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:00,640
I was so worried about you.

91
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:02,960
You lost your memory.

92
00:09:04,400 --> 00:09:05,200
But...

93
00:09:06,760 --> 00:09:08,280
part of me felt relieved.

94
00:09:10,640 --> 00:09:11,720
What gave me hope

95
00:09:13,400 --> 00:09:15,640
was that it gave us a
chance to start over.

96
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:18,560
But what broke my heart

97
00:09:19,680 --> 00:09:21,320
was that all those
beautiful memories we shared

98
00:09:22,760 --> 00:09:24,160
were remembered by me alone.

99
00:09:26,920 --> 00:09:27,920
It's been three years.

100
00:09:29,880 --> 00:09:31,640
I thought I'd become a better person.

101
00:09:35,200 --> 00:09:37,240
But I never expected
that I'd still be this cowardly.

102
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:49,200
I know you hate me.

103
00:09:50,880 --> 00:09:52,680
And I hate who I am now, too.

104
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:57,320
So.

105
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:00,680
we really did have

106
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:03,600
a lot of happy times together,

107
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:05,800
didn't we?

108
00:10:49,814 --> 00:10:51,884
♪We say good morning, we say good night♪

109
00:10:51,884 --> 00:10:55,304
♪We say we miss each other,
but never speak of the hurt♪

110
00:10:56,904 --> 00:10:58,794
♪The sweeter it is, the luckier we seem♪

111
00:10:58,794 --> 00:11:02,784
♪Yet the more romantic,
the rougher the road♪

112
00:11:04,024 --> 00:11:05,884
♪Let me go, set me free♪

113
00:11:05,884 --> 00:11:09,924
♪Let me drown in reckless silence♪

114
00:11:10,464 --> 00:11:15,874
♪We were perfect for each other,
yet you never admitted it♪

115
00:11:17,224 --> 00:11:19,364
♪The freedom you gave me♪

116
00:11:19,364 --> 00:11:23,004
♪Became the heaviest chain I bear♪

117
00:11:24,264 --> 00:11:26,534
♪Love can barely move forward♪

118
00:11:26,534 --> 00:11:30,314
♪Yet the words still linger unspoken♪

119
00:11:31,414 --> 00:11:33,654
♪The closeness I long for♪

120
00:11:33,654 --> 00:11:38,044
♪There's no need for you
to keep avoiding it♪

121
00:11:38,454 --> 00:11:40,274
♪I don't want to break free♪

122
00:11:40,274 --> 00:11:45,644
♪Take back the chains
disguised as freedom♪

